==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cottonwood
<hw>Cot"ton*wood`</hw> <pr>(-w⟦oocr⟧d`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An American tree of the genus <gen>Populus</gen>
or poplar, having the seeds covered with abundant cottonlike hairs;
esp., the <spn>Populus monilifera</spn> and <spn>Populus
angustifolia</spn> of the Western United States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cottony</ent>⟦br⟧
